<plot>The smoldering young Amitabh Bachchan plays Vijay, the illegitimate child of a wealthy businessman (Amjad Khan) and a beautiful singer (Rakhee). Abandoned as an infant and raised largely by a shiftless drunk (Shreeram Lagoo), Vijay is now grown up and, unbeknown st to everyone, working for his own father. In order to marry his true love Mohini (Zeenat Aman), however, he's going to have to find out what his true ancestry is--even if doing so throws everybody's life into chaos.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?317291</url></doc>
